  "description": "Aberdeen Group corporate background slide deck (v9-19) used for outbound marketing \u2014 client meetings, new-hire orientation, and investor briefings. Three offices (Boston, Palo Alto, Amsterdam), aberdeen.com URL. Four-slide structure: (1) title; (2) Aberdeen's Market Positioning; (3) Aberdeen's Competitive Landscape; (4) business architecture diagram mapping IT Supplier Executives and Private Equity audiences through Services, Practice Areas, Surveys/Field Instruments, Emerging Market Intelligence, Webcasts/Conferences/Seminars, aberdeen.com aggregation, Supplier Meetings, e-Learning, Field Sales, and Marketing Consulting. Primary text extraction is sparse \u2014 the deck is diagram-heavy.",
